('90105', '2017-01-05', 'Language and Administrative Assistant', 'Full Time', '5', 'The OSCE Office in Yerevan invites applications from\r\rhighly qualified energetic and experienced Armenian professionals for\r\rthe post of Language and Administrative Assistant.', 'Under supervision of the Head of Office the\r\rincumbent will perform the following tasks: \r\r- Provide high quality written translations of draft laws regulations\r\rcomments to legislation reports other documents/ correspondence from\r\rArmenian and Russian into English and vice versa for all programmes of\r\rthe office;\r\r- Act as interpreter for the office staff and other OSCE officials as\r\rand when needed at meetings/ conferences;\r\r- Arrange appointments for the Head of Office and draft routine\r\rcorrespondence for him/her;\r\r- Maintain proper electronic and paper filing systems;\r\r- Perform other related duties as requited.', 455, 80000, 110000, ''),
