('92389', '2017-04-29', 'Automated Test Engineer', 'Full Time', '9', 'The primary objective of this position is automation\r\rof testing process to ensure the quality of CQG products. Automated Test\r\rEngineer will perform wide range of automated testing and work with test\r\rdocumentation.', '- Design and code automated testing scripts;\r\r- Create test plans from requirements and design documents;\r\r- Record test results;\r\r- Identify reproduce and report defects;\r\r- Maintain test plans;\r\r- Test defect fixes.', 25, 65000, 95000, ''),
